HEADWORD: homogenized
<hw>homogenized</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>formed by blending
unlike elements, especially by reducing one element to particles and
dispersing them throughout another substance.</def>
<hascons>homogeneous</hascons>⟦br⟧
